---
// SplitFeature.astro
---
<section class="section split-section">
  <div class="container container-split">
    <div class="split-left dark-card">
      <div class="shield-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</div>
      <h2>100% Anti-Detect — Akun Kamu <span class="text-gradient">Tetap Aman</span></h2>
      <p class="desc">
        Sistem kami mensimulasikan aktivitas manusia secara organik sesuai parameter TikTok Studio. 
        Bebas blokir massal dan proxy detector — keamanan akun adalah prioritas utama kami.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="split-right">
      <div class="card right-card h-effect">
        <div class="r-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</div>
        <div class="r-text">
          <h3>Browser Anti-Fingerprint & RPA</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Kombinasi teknologi browser khusus dan otomasi proses robotik (RPA) untuk memastikan setiap upload terlihat alami dan tidak terdeteksi sebagai bot.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card right-card h-effect">
        <div class="r-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌐</div>
        <div class="r-text">
          <h3 class="os-icons">
            Full OS Compatibility
            <span class="icons-row" aria-label="Tersedia untuk Mac dan Windows">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 448 512" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M0 93.7l183.6-25.3v177.4H0V93.7zm0 324.6l183.6 25.3V268.4H0v149.9zm203.8 28L448 480V268.4H203.8v177.9zm0-380.6v180.1H448V32L203.8 65.7z"/></svg>
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 384 512" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M318.7 268.7c-.2-36.7 16.4-64.4 50-84.8-18.8-26.9-47.2-41.7-84.7-44.6-35.5-2.8-74.3 20.7-88.5 20.7-15 0-49.4-19.7-76.4-19.7C63.3 141.2 4 184.8 4 273.5q0 39.3 14.4 81.2c12.8 36.7 59 126.7 107.2 125.2 25.2-.6 43-17.9 75.8-17.9 31.8 0 48.3 17.9 76.4 17.9 48.6-.7 90.4-82.5 102.6-119.3-65.2-30.7-61.7-90-61.7-91.9zm-56.6-164.2c27.3-32.4 24.8-61.9 24-72.5-24.1 1.4-52 16.4-67.9 34.9-17.5 19.8-27.8 44.3-25.6 71.9 26.1 2 49.9-11.4 69.5-34.3z"/></svg>
            </span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Software handal yang kompatibel sepenuhnya dengan Windows dan macOS. Siap mengeksekusi upload massal secara instan dari perangkat Anda.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="promo-box">
        🚀 <strong>Investasi Sekali:</strong> Akses Selamanya & Update Gratis.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .split-section {
    background-color: #fcfcfc;
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .container-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .dark-card {
    background: #111827;
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 60px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .shield-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .dark-card h2 {
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .dark-card .desc {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .split-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .right-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 32px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    background: white;
  }

  .r-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--primary);
    border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
  }

  .r-text h3 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .os-icons {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .icons-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .h-effect:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .promo-box {
    margin-top: 12px;
    background: #eff6ff;
    border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .container-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .split-section { padding: 60px 0; }
    .dark-card { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .dark-card h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .shield-icon { width: 60px; height: 60px; font-size: 2rem; }
    .right-card { padding: 24px 20px; gap: 16px; flex-direction: row; }
    .r-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .r-text h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .r-text p { font-size: 0.9rem; }
  }
</style>
